      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Benchmark problems from NAFEMS and internal test suite confirm correct implementation of linear elastic constitutive models and contact algorithms used in the pedicle screw construct simulation."
    },
    {
