      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Simulation protocol peer-reviewed by two independent analysts. Input deck reviewed against ASTM F1717 boundary condition specifications. No discrepancies identified between intended and implemented model configuration."
