      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level for model risk level 3.",
      "rationale": "Linear elastic material models applied to titanium alloy components consistent with published material characterization data. Contact formulation captures load transfer at screw-rod interface. Model form appropriate for monotonic quasi-static compression-bending loading regime."
    },
