      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Material properties sourced from manufacturer certificates of conformance and published literature for Ti-6Al-4V ELI. Geometric inputs derived from CMM measurements of physical constructs. Torque values for set screws measured during specimen preparation and applied as pre-loads."
    },
