      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Quantitative comparison performed using mean absolute percentage error (MAPE) and Bland-Altman analysis for construct stiffness and peak displacement at failure load. MAPE < 8% across all specimens. Statistical equivalence confirmed at 95% confidence interval."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
