    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for model risk level 3. The single deficiency in Test conditions (achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is acknowledged and documented. The overall evidence body is judged sufficient to support medium assurance for the intended compression-bending performance prediction application. The assessment team accepts the credibility package with the noted limitation in test condition coverage.",
